s.t: Playing at the highest U15 level
Tom dreams of being as good as
Playing at the highest U15 level
and he is working hard to overcome this
One year ago he started playing with
a prosthesis to achieve his goals
Getting use to the prosthesis has been
his biggest challenge in his career so far
This season Tom's been on fire,
with three goals and seven assists
Promising to do everything in their power
to help him develop as a player
discovered him at a young age,
but weren't convinced by his potential
